  * debian/: Apply "wrap-and-sort -abst".
  * debian/control:
    + Remove unnecessary build-dependency.
    + Bump Standards-Version to 4.4.0.
    + Bump debhelper compat to v12.
    + Update homepage since the project has migrated.
  * debian/watch: Also monitor new upstream release page.
  * debian/rules: Remove override for dh_strip since the migration
    has completed.

